
## using the rating prediction can easily help coaches and Scouts for the following :

* Display Analytics & Stats: Use ratings to visualize performance trends over time.

* Track Player Progress: Monitor rating changes to show improvement.

* Compare Players in Same Position: Ratings help compare players' performance.

* Analyze Playing Style & Suggest Teams: Ratings identify strengths and team fit.

* Recommend Team Formation: Use ratings to build the optimal lineup.

* Player Development: AI insights based on ratings highlight improvement areas.

* Optimize Recruitment: Assess player compatibility with team needs via ratings.

* Assist Coaches & Scouts: Real-time ratings support decision-making.
